- ðŸ” **Search Albums** â€“ Search for albums by artist or title via the Last.fm API  
- ðŸ’¾ **Save Favorites** â€“ Save albums locally to view later, even when offline  
- ðŸ–¼ï¸ **Album Details** â€“ View album information and cover art  
- ðŸ“² **SwiftUI Interface** â€“ Built entirely with SwiftUI for a modern, reactive UI  
- ðŸ“¦ **Local Storage** â€“ Uses SwiftData for saving favorite albums locally  

